A **media query** applies styles conditionally based on device characteristics.
```css
@media (max-width: 768px) { ... }
```

CSS **animations** gradually change element styles using keyframes.
```css
@keyframes name { from { } to { } }
```

**@import** brings in external stylesheets or modules.
```css
@import url("styles.css");
```

```scss
@function name($param1, $param2) { @return value; }
```
Defines a custom function that computes and returns a value using @return, callable anywhere a CSS value is expected for dynamic calculations within stylesheets.

```scss
@each $var in list | @each $key, $value in map { ... }
```
Iterates over items in a list or key-value pairs in a map, generating CSS rules for each iteration, commonly used for producing utility classes or theme variations.
